            "review_text": "Where do I begin with this one. This game, played a huge part in my childhood. I started playing late but when I finally got more into it oh boy, I loved it even more than ever. Overall amazing game, while it has its flaws and may not be everyone's cup of tea, for me personally, as a person who grew up watching sfm's and Gmod animations it's a must play."
