            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "The utmost greatest game I in my personal experience that I call my life, have ever had the honor of engaging in play with during my lifespan in my mortal shell of a meat enclosure. This game expanded the horizons of my feeble human mind. This game -which by the way is an understatement at best, calling this masterpiece a mere game- showed me The Great Beyond™ and much more. The combination of ones and zeros that make up this heavenly blessing has poured inside my dna and merged with me forever and irreversibly. I am cleansed. I am purified. I am more..."
