            "review_text": "A good game to hang out and have fun with your friends, the interactions are funny and timeless, and so many ways to play. with plenty of games modes to satisfy anyone's play style.\r\nalso good to give yourself heart palpitations out of rage when you hit a dead centre shot with the scattergun only for it to spark and get you killed   \r\n"
